'''大衛·洛厄尔·戴维斯'''（{{lang-en|'''David Lowell Davis'''}}，{{bd|1991年|2月20日|catidx=Davids, David}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場_(足球)|中場]]，現時效力[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]。

==球員生涯==
===狼隊===
戴维斯在2008年從[[特維德勒足球會|特維德勒]]轉投[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]青年軍，2009年5月簽下職業合約。同年10月24日在外借[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|达灵顿]]期間首次在職業聯賽中上場。

2010年9月，他被外借至[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|沃尔索尔]]六星期<ref>{{cite news|title=Wolverhampton Wanderers David Davis agrees Walsall loan|date=9 September 2010|publisher=BBC Sport|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/walsall/8984710.stm}}</ref>。2011年1月31日，他被外借至[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|谢斯伯利]]<ref>{{cite news| title =Wolves loan young midfielder David Davis to Shrews|publisher =BBC Sport| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/shrewsbury/9382675.stm| date =31 January 2011}}</ref>，後來租借期延長至季末<ref>{{cite news|title=Contracts finalised for young quintet|date=24 March 2011|publisher=wolves.co.uk|url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~2323035,00.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120908082451/http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/News/0,,10307~2323035,00.html|archivedate=2012年9月8日|accessdate=2014年10月15日}}</ref>。

2011/12球季，戴维斯繼續他的外借生涯，這次是[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[因弗内斯足球俱乐部|因弗内斯]]，租借期為2011年8月31日至1月9日<ref>{{cite news| title =Wolves' David Davis joins Inverness on loan|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/14732205.stm| publisher =BBC Sport| date =31 August 2011}}</ref>，然而戴维斯拒絕繼續留在因弗内斯，租借期滿後回到狼隊<ref>{{cite news| title =Wolves' David Davis ends Inverness stay|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/16429081.stm| publisher =BBC Sport| date =5 January 2012}}</ref>。2012年1月，他被外借至[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|切斯特菲尔德]]<ref>{{cite news| title =Chesterfield sign Wolves midfielder David Davis on loan|publisher =BBC Sport| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/16549941.stm| date=13 January 2012}}</ref>，不久之後被母會召回以彌補受傷球員的位置。2012年3月10日對[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布莱克本流浪者]]的比賽中，他被安排上場參賽，是他首場[[英超|英超]]比賽，最終狼隊以2-0落敗。這球季戴维斯共有7次英超上場紀錄，但狼隊最終仍以聯賽副班長姿態降級<ref>{{cite news| title=David Davis set for Premier League debut| publisher=Express & Star| url=http://www.expressandstar.com/sport/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2012/03/07/david-davis-set-for-premier-league-debut/| date=7 March 2012| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2016-03-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045021/http://www.expressandstar.com/sport/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2012/03/07/david-davis-set-for-premier-league-debut/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。季末他與球會簽下一份三年新合約，至2015年完結<ref>{{cite news|title=Wolverhampton Wanderers' David Davis signs new three-year deal|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17844916|publisher=BBC Sport|date=25 April 2012|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-date=2015-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104175912/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17844916|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012/13球季，戴维斯獲得不少上場機會。2013年3月對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托尔城]]賽事中，他接到[[卡爾·伊克梅|卡爾·伊克梅]]的球門球時受壓回傳給伊克梅，伊克梅判斷錯誤使戴维斯無辜地打進[[烏龍球|烏龍球]]，布里斯托尔城取得領先，但狼隊最後以2-1反勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/262378/report |title=Championship: Wolves come from behind to seal 2-1 win over Bristol City |publisher=Sky Sports |date=16 March 2013 |accessdate=2 September 2014 |archive-date=2013-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130612094859/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/262378/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。戴维斯在4月6日對[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]的賽事中受傷，提前告別球季，而狼隊最終亦保級失敗降至英甲<ref>{{cite news| title=David Davis: Wolves midfielder likely to be the latest to miss run-in| publisher=BBC Sport| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22080900| date=9 April 2013| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2013-04-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414054342/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22080900| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013/14球季，戴维斯不受到新教練[[肯尼·杰基特|肯尼·杰基特]]的器重，並沒有獲得很多的比賽機會，球季最後三個月更是被排除在比賽名單。球會曾嘗試把他外借至[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|巴恩斯利]]，但最終告吹<ref>{{cite news| title=Wolves' David Davis sees Barnsley loan switch fall through| publisher=Sky Sports| url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11688/9394636/transfer-news-wolves-david-davis-sees-barnsley-loan-switch-fall-through| date=25 July 2014| accessdate=2014-10-15| archive-date=2016-03-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306063735/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11688/9394636/transfer-news-wolves-david-davis-sees-barnsley-loan-switch-fall-through| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===伯明翰城===
2014年8月11日，戴维斯轉投鄰城的英冠球會[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]，作為[[汤姆·阿德耶米|汤姆·阿德耶米]]的代替者，簽約兩年並有一年行使權<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140811-official-blues-bring-in-david-davis-1819172.aspx |title=Official: Blues bring in David Davis |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=11 August 2014 |accessdate=13 August 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812004853/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/20140811-official-blues-bring-in-david-davis-1819172.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。翌日在英格蘭聯賽盃賽事便代表球隊上場對[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|剑桥联]]<ref name=sb1415>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=52649&season_id=144 |title=Games played by David Davis in 2014/2015 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=5 October 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629045309/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=52649&season_id=144 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以後成為了球隊的主力球員。10月4日對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查尔顿竞技]]的比賽中打進在球會首顆進球，最終以1-1戰平<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/updated-charlton-1-birmingham-city-7883640 |title=Charlton 1 Birmingham City 1 |last=Tattum |first=Colin |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=4 October 2014 |accessdate=5 October 2014 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924201510/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/updated-charlton-1-birmingham-city-7883640 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

